column1: Assigning lat-longs to AA/CREST biological sample data

issue:  many locations used in logs and by observers are not listed in CREST and so don't have any ability to geo-reference.   The yellow is the proposed work to identify lat-longs for each location used.
there were about 780 such location names.   Cursory review identified suitable locations for about 300.   480 location names remain which need some lat-longs.
the task is to fill in the 480 blank or #NA rows in columns K-O.   Or at least as many as possible.   Some will not be possible.
